  "title": "Fallback on hierarchicalFacet",
  "body": "If you don't declare your facet correctly in a widget config, it ends up using the hierarchical facet in place of giving a precise error.\n\nexample of wrong syntax -> 'facet' : ['lang'] in place of ['facet']:['lang']\n\nDon't know if you can do something with that. But it would definitely have helped me to get some help here.\n",
